SUMMARY:Nature Tales: Spring Beauties
DESCRIPTION:Register Here\n\nAges: 3-7 with accompanying adult\nDate: Friday\, May 8\nTime: 10:00 – 11:00 a.m.\nLocation: North Carolina Botanical Garden\nFee: Free; pre-registration required. \n  \nSpring is bursting with color! Find a place on our blanket for stories about flowers and their busy pollinators\, then take a walk with us through the Garden to see the native blooms up close. \nThe program will happen rain or shine\, with indoor activities if the weather is unfavorable. This family-friendly program has been designed especially for children ages 3-7. \n  \nRegister Here
