SUMMARY:60th Anniversary Gala
DESCRIPTION:  \nMay 15\, 2026\n \nBuy Tickets \nFrom protecting native plants to inspiring generations of visitors\, the Garden continues to grow because of you. Join us for an evening of celebration as we honor what we’ve accomplished and share our vision for the future: where science\, engagement\, and conservation come together with purpose and possibility. \n \n  \n \nHonorary Chairs\nRitch & Susan Allison\nFrank & Ellen Proctor\nMike & Melissa Raley \nPlanning Committee\nGail Perry\nPat Holder\nMelanie Christian\nJordan Barratt\nBetsy Bennett\nMay Bryan\nVirginia Buysse\nEliza Cook\nKim Fraser\nHelen Frankstone\nKatherine Kopp\nSue Plambeck\nMia Pizzagalli\nLiza Roberts \n \nEvent Hosts\nLongleaf\nFrank & Ellen Proctor \nMagnolia\nJeff Mason\nSue & Charles Plambeck \nSassafras\nBetsy & Walter Bennett\nBecky & Munroe Cobey\nNicholas & Amy Penwarden\nGail Perry & Bill Cobb \nDogwood\nSims Preston & Olympia Stone\nCarol Tresolini & Tom Fiore \nFor information on becoming an Event Host see this link or contact Stephen Keith at 919-962-9458. \nBuy Tickets
URL:https://ncbg.unc.edu/event/60th-anniversary-gala/
LOCATION:The Barn at Fearrington Village\, 2000 Fearrington Village Center\, Pittsboro\, 27312\, United States
END:VEVENT
